{"tid":1529313,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"外資到依家都唔撒出香港既原因原來係咁","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T19:16:06.000Z","uid":277873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dbda2a89d95bb2f3be0526d5c1911cb38aa8cff9","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"點解香港已經死人冧樓，都仲未有人撒資？<br />\n因為佢哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇死我哋班香港人就算死人冧樓都會照返工呀！</span></span><br />\n對所有大老闆嚟講，只要啲奴隸準時返工幫佢賺錢，佢理得你屋企死咗幾多人？<br />\n咁如果就連警察同黑社會周街斬人大家都會準時返工，係黨鐵畀人打到仆街甚至唔見咗幾個，大家都係會準時返工，咁佢哋點會唔相信就算解放軍入城，香港人第二日都一樣係會照樣返工？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">既然對佢哋根本無影響，咁佢哋仲駛鬼撒資？仲講乜攬炒？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家睇吓富臨，只要齊心罷，真係會有效果！齊心，堅持，比啲耐性！比啲掙扎！<br />\n全民大罷工啊！"},{"pid":"d32d1eccc8cc6161d0fd7697055bbe15a8362fbb","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"推上去！"},{"pid":"86cfba219da2a4e7d84cfc47470a8d0092f5118a","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"663020583b975ab4863bb768c33becda80191760","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"推三罷！"},{"pid":"f25e3bdb67ad992b1ee5947fbcfec3a80185c0a4","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"幫手推上去"},{"pid":"9ea1f6f2809d4286aa753ef183745d0e9a51ef41","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b760f9c789e607db3d5db01501abf03aacf0765","tid":1529313,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:41:54.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"fa5a631e5788c7121120cb50d8398cba695c74ec","tid":1529313,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019